          "label": "Lithium Iron Phosphate / LFP (1.10x — longest lifespan)"
        },
        {
          "value": "lead-acid",
          "label": "Lead-Acid (0.65x — budget, shorter lifespan)"
        }
      ],
      "helpText": "NMC is most common (Tesla, Enphase). LFP lasts longer with more cycles. Lead-acid is cheapest but has a shorter usable life."
    },
    {
