  "formulaSource": "Battery capacity pricing from HomeAdvisor, Angi, and EnergySage marketplace data 2025-2026. Chemistry multipliers from manufacturer MSRP comparisons (Tesla, Enphase, Generac, LG). Inverter and transfer switch pricing from HomeAdvisor 2025-2026 national surveys. Electrical upgrade costs from HomeAdvisor panel upgrade cost data. IRA 30% tax credit per IRC §25D as extended by the Inflation Reduction Act through 2032. Backup hour estimates based on average US residential consumption of ~30 kWh/day (EIA). Regional labor multipliers derived from BLS OES regional wage data for electricians (SOC 47-2111).",
